@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jjlefx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin(tmp) * 0.90)
    v2 = (0.98 * (wp.cos(v1 + 0.61) / (v0 + 0.88 / v2 + 0.83)))
    v1 = (0.22 * tmp)
    tmp = wp.cos((v1 / (v2 + 0.62 / v1 + 0.32)))
    v0 = v2
    v2 = 0.67
    data[tid] = v0
